Supplemental Constraint (DR-TOE Two-Stage Open-Source Rule)
1. Two-Stage Creation Logic
Stage 1 Original Attribution Confirmation: All core differential equations, cross-scale isomorphic models, six-category evolutionary discriminant logic are independent original achievements derived from DR-TOE dimensional reciprocity axioms. The author reserves exclusive original attribution right to define open-source rules, to prevent the framework from being intercepted, split and privatized.
Stage 2 Public Inclusive Sharing: After attribution confirmation, all simulation code, core mathematical models are permanently incorporated into human public domain. All individuals and institutions can use, modify and develop freely without exclusive patent authorization.

2. Exclusive Patent Prohibition
The cross-scale hierarchical dissipation dynamic framework, differential system, lifespan closed formula, six end-state classification in this repository have been fully disclosed in Zenodo preprint (corresponding DOI). Any party is prohibited from applying any exclusive patent based on the code, model and theory contained herein. All relevant patent applications shall be deemed invalid due to loss of novelty, and this open-source repository together with preprint is absolute defense evidence.

3. Traceability Requirement
Any derivative modification, secondary development and dissemination must retain original author, ORCID: 0009-0006-66691790, and preprint DOI link.
